VSAP-Server-Modules-vsap-config version 0.01
============================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL INSTALLDIRS=vendor
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  blah blah blah

